<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;<br />
&lt;html&gt;<br />
&lt;body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f6f9; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; color:#1f2937;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &lt;table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f4f6f9; padding:30px 0;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td align="center"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td style="background:#0f4c81; color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:24px; font-size:24px; font-weight:bold;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Application Update<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td style="padding:32px;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;p style="margin:0 0 16px; font-size:16px;"&gt;Hello {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/p&gt;<br />
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;p style="margin:0 0 16px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; We are pleased to inform you that your application has progressed to the next stage of our recruitment process.<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;<br />
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;p style="margin:0 0 16px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Your profile has been reviewed successfully, and your interview process has now been initiated.<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;<br />
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;p style="margin:0; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Our team will contact you soon with the interview details and any additional instructions.<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td style="background:#f9fafb; padding:20px 32px; font-size:13px; color:#6b7280; text-align:center;"&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Best regards,&lt;br&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;strong&gt;Recruitment Team&lt;/strong&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/table&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;<br />
&nbsp; &lt;/table&gt;<br />
&lt;/body&gt;<br />
&lt;/html&gt;</body>
</html>